"Esta carpeta tiene varias subcarpetas. La carpeta ``portal_skins`` tiene "
"una propiedad que define en qué orden Plone busca atributos u objetos en "
"cada subcarpeta."

#: ../mastering-plone/extending.rst:144
msgid "The Plone logo is in a skin folder."
msgstr "El logo de Plone está en una carpeta de skin."

#: ../mastering-plone/extending.rst:146
msgid ""
"By default, your site has a ``custom`` folder, and items are first "
"searched for in that folder."
msgstr ""
"Por defecto, su sitio tiene una carpeta ``custom``, y los elementos se "
"buscan primero en esa carpeta."

#: ../mastering-plone/extending.rst:148
msgid ""
"To customize the logo, you copy it into the ``custom`` folder, and change"
" it there. This way you can change templates, CSS styles, images and "
"behavior, because a container may contain Python scripts."
msgstr ""
"Para personalizar el logotipo, cópielo en la carpeta ``custom`` y "
