"imágenes y comportamiento, ya que un contenedor puede contener scripts de"
" Python."

#: ../mastering-plone/extending.rst:150
msgid ""
"Skin-folder style customization may be accomplished TTW via the ZMI, or "
"with add-on packages. Many older-style packages create their own skin "
"folder and add it to the skin layer for Plone when installed."
msgstr ""
